ry Act. Provides that the Department of State Police may develop a system under which the holder of a concealed carry license may display an electronic version of his or her license on a mobile telephone or other portable electronic device. Provides that an electronic version of a license shall contain security features the Department determines to be necessary to ensure that the electronic version is accurate and current and shall satisfy other requirements the Department determines to be necessary regarding form and content. Provides that the display or possession of an electronic version of a license in accordance with the requirements of the Department satisfies all requirements for the display or possession of a valid license under the laws of this State. Makes conforming changes.", "pending_committee_id": 0, "committee": [], "referrals": [{"date": "2018-02-14", "committee_id": 254, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Assignments"}, {"date": "2018-02-21", "committee_id": 277, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Judiciary"}, {"date": "2018-04-27", "committee_id": 254, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Assignments"}], "history": [{"date": "2018-02-14", "action": "Filed with Secretary by Sen. Neil Anderson", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2018-02-14", "action": "First Reading", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2018-02-14", "action": "Referred to Assignments", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2018-02-21", "action": "Assigned to Judiciary", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2018-02-22", "action": "Added as Co-Sponsor Sen. Jennifer Bertino-Tarrant", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2018-02-22", "action": "Added as Co-Sponsor Sen. James F. Clayborne, Jr.", "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2018-02-22", "action": "Added as Co-Sponsor Sen. Elgie R. Sims, Jr.", "chamber": "S", 